: "events.event", "pk": 23, "fields": {"host": 6, "title": "Cyber Security with Ethical Hacking | 2 Day Workshop at IIST Thiruvananthapuram", "description": "Tech Workshop Series 2026 with Globally Recognized Certification.\r\n\r\n\r\nContent will be covered from basic to advance level.\r\n\r\n\r\nEligibility\r\n\r\nOpen to all!\r\n\r\nB.Tech, B.E., BCA, MCA, B.Sc IT, M.Sc IT, MBBS, MS, MD, Biomedical, Biotechnology, BBA, MBA, B.A., and hobbyists from all backgrounds\r\n\r\n\r\nSessions : Introduction to Ethical Hacking & Cyber Security, Overview of ethical hacking, Understanding the role of cybersecurity in protecting individuals and organizations, Different types of hackers, Scope and limitations of ethical hacking", "date": "2026-01-25T11:30:00Z", "location": "Indian Institute of Space Science and Technology, Thiruvananthapuram, Thiruvananthapuram", "event_image": "event_images/event-8.png", "category": "tech", "approval_status": "approved", "created_at": "2026-01-16T12:50:43.370Z"}}, {"model": "events.event", "pk": 24, "fields": {"host": 6, "title": "Generative & Agentic AI | 2 Day Workshop at IIST Thiruvananthapuram", "description": "Tech Workshop Series 2026 with Globally Recognized Certification.\r\n\r\n\r\nContent will be covered from basic to advanced level.\r\n\r\n\r\nMastering Generative and Agentic AI: Creative Intelligence in Action\r\n\r\nIntroduction to Generative AI\r\n\r\nUnderstand what Generative AI (GenAI) is\r\n\r\nDistinguish between AI, machine learning, and deep learning.\r\n\r\nDiscriminative AI vs. Generative AI & Agentic AI\r\n\r\nOverview of tools used in GenAI\r\n\r\nExplore privileged GenAI tools and models\r\n\r\nRoadmap to explore GenAI models", "date": "2026-01-25T12:00:00Z", "location": "Indian Institute of Space Science and Technology, Thiruvananthapuram, Thiruvananthapuram", "event_image": "event_images/event-9.png", "category": "tech", "approval_status": "approved", "created_at": "2026-01-16T12:52:28.778Z"}}, {"model": "events.ev